a.n: WKF Championships 2016 Linz, Austria, Saturday Session Highlights (1)

p.d: The 2016 WKF World Karate Championships bring together the most established karate practitioners on the planet to decide who is the best of the best. Emanating from Austria, this edition of the World Karate Championships will decide the winners in 10 different weight categories for both men and women in the kumite (fighting) portion.
